[Several more cases are reported. It is not yet known how many potentially contaminated vials were distributed and used. Likewise, no further information has been made available about the fungus isolated in one patient and if it was isolated from other patients or any unused vials. - Mod.LL

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1hiS.]
